tdo_attributes_description: TRUST_ATTRIBUTE_NON_TRANSITIVE - dom A trust only dom B, dom A does not trust C throught dom B if dom B trust dom C
TRUST_ATTRIBUTE_UPLEVEL_ONLY - only win2000/newer can use this link
TRUST_ATTRIBUTE_QUARANTINED_DOMAIN - Domain is quarantined and subject to the rules of SID filtering
TRUST_ATTRIBUTE_FOREST_TRANSITIVE - cross forest trust between root forest.
TRUST_ATTRIBUTE_CROSS_ORGANIZATION - trust to domain or forest not part of organization
TRUST_ATTRIBUTE_WITHIN_FOREST - trust within the same forest
TRUST_ATTRIBUTE_TREAT_AS_EXTERNAL - cross forest trust but external
TRUST_ATTRIBUTE_CROSS_ORGANIZATION_NO_TGT_DELEGATION - trust must not be trusted for delegation
TRUST_ATTRIBUTE_PIM_TRUST - trust treated as Privileged Identity Management
